{"tid":185592,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"93-98瘋狂吃喝玩樂吹水活動谷","createTime":"2017-04-03T14:26:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-10T01:17:18.000Z","uid":85996,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"83681a5d490ddbf257885b4d3611eb1c01cc9ddd","tid":185592,"uid":85996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T14:26:15.000Z","msg":"咁多位巴絲想唔想擴闊自己既社交圈子呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家機會黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n歡迎鐘意瘋狂吹水既巴絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我地會瘋狂搞活動  總之你肯join我地肯搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n亦都十分歡迎自組活動或即興約食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望巴絲比例一比一  最少十人成團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嚴禁狗公 娘娘 杜絕小圈子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋會定期加新人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我地會儲埋一次過加人 麻煩留左資料既巴絲請耐心等待<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1rHNGdHexnj_ISSmpatFl76jnOFqkgnBo4bQu4K4m8jU/edit\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2F1rHNGdHexnj_ISSmpatFl76jnOFqkgnBo4bQu4K4m8jU%2Fedit&d=HQiZr%2BzFLDuBt%2FA%2FXRO5Itr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=308a3972\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1rHNGdHexnj_ISSmpatFl76jnOFqkgnBo4bQu4K4m8jU/edit</a>"},{"pid":"000fe0b3322ec3c6e7d753acf7fc87860ab98698","tid":185592,"uid":85996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T14:35:34.000Z",